---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Professional profile of Miguel Ramirez Exojo in cloud, DevOps and infrastructure."
>
  <section class="page-head section">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>Cloud, DevOps and infrastructure focused on stable operations.</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Work on design, operation and improvement of technical platforms for companies
      needing progress without adding unnecessary complexity to their teams.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section prose-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Summary</p>
      <h2>Over 19 years in systems, cloud and infrastructure.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="prose-stack">
      <p>
        I'm Miguel Ramirez Exojo. Work with AWS, GCP, Azure, OpenStack, and Linux
        environments to deploy, automate and maintain secure, sustainable platforms.
        Core focus: Infrastructure as Code, cloud operations, continuous improvement.
      </p>
      <p>
        Typical stack: Terraform, Ansible, Kubernetes, Docker, CI/CD and automation
        aimed at reducing manual work. Public certifications: Terraform, LPIC-3 Linux,
        OpenStack. Collaborate with industrial SMEs and IT companies needing advanced
        technical support.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" aria-label="Experience summary">
    <div class="about-ledger">
      <article>
        <span>01</span>
        <h3>Current focus</h3>
        <p>Managed cloud, automation, observability and operational continuity.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <span>02</span>
        <h3>Technologies</h3>
        <p>Terraform, Ansible, Kubernetes, Docker, Linux, AWS, GCP, Azure and OpenStack.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <span>03</span>
        <h3>Collaboration</h3>
        <p>Remote work across EMEA and support for both end-clients and technology partners.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section prose-grid about-closing">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Method</p>
      <h2>Solve first, complicate less.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="prose-stack">
      <p>
        I focus on making infrastructure useful for business and easy to operate:
        clear decisions, repeatable deployments, understandable costs and real recovery
        capability when something fails.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
